OL,3,CNew silverback takes charge after
OL,4,Cdeath of oldest male gorilla in UK
OL,6,FA new silverback has taken charge
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of the UK's oldest
OL,8,Fgorilla.
OL,10,FNkoumou has arrived at Bristol Zoo
OL,11,FProject to lead the zoo's troop of six
OL,12,Fwestern lowland gorillas.
OL,14,FAs a silverback, Nkoumou will become
OL,15,Fthe troop's main peacekeeper and
OL,16,Fprotector, helping maintain stability
OL,17,Fwithin the family group.
OL,19,FNkoumou succeeds Jock, the much-loved
OL,20,Fsilverback who died earlier this year
OL,21,Faged 42.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
