PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782400702
OL,3,CNew silverback takes charge after
OL,4,Cdeath of oldest male gorilla in UK
OL,6,FJock was the oldest male gorilla in
OL,7,Fthe UK and led Bristol's gorilla troop
OL,8,Ffor more than two decades.
OL,10,FThe move from Port Lympne Hotel &
OL,11,FReserve in Kent is part of a
OL,12,Fconservation breeding programme to
OL,13,Fhelp safeguard the future of western
OL,14,Flowland gorillas.
OL,16,FTransporting a 180kg silverback
OL,17,Fgorilla from Kent to his new home at
OL,18,FBristol Zoo Project required months of
OL,19,Fcareful planning.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782400702
OL,3,CNew silverback takes charge after
OL,4,Cdeath of oldest male gorilla in UK
OL,6,FOver the coming months, Nkoumou will
OL,7,Fbe gradually introduced to the zoo's
OL,8,Ftroop through a carefully managed
OL,9,Fprocess overseen by animal keepers and
OL,10,Fwelfare experts.
OL,12,FWestern lowland gorillas live in close-
OL,13,Fknit family groups with complex social
OL,14,Frelationships, meaning introductions
OL,15,Fcan take weeks or months as new bonds
OL,16,Fand relationships are established.
OL,18,FThe name Nkoumou comes from a central
OL,19,FAfrican word ` "Nkumu" (Na-ku-mu)
OL,20,Fwhich means "leader".
OL,26,@{D@POU{D@VO]|D@MOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
