OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782400702
OL,3,CNew silverback takes charge after
OL,4,Cdeath of oldest male gorilla in UK
OL,6,FThe addition of "ou" is a homage to
OL,7,FNkoumou's father ` "Djanghou". Nkoumou
OL,8,Fis also a village in Gabon.
OL,10,FThe troop comprises three adult
OL,11,Ffemales Touni, Kera and Kala,
OL,12,Fadolescent female Ayana and juvenile
OL,13,Fmales Juni and Hasani.
OL,15,FBrian Zimmerman, director of
OL,16,Fconservation and science at Bristol
OL,17,FZoological Society, said: "Nkoumou's
OL,18,Farrival is significant not only for
OL,19,FBristol Zoo Project, but for the
OL,20,Ffuture of a species under threat in
OL,21,Fthe wild.
OL,26,@nD@QOUnD@TO]oD@TOUoD@]O]yD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
