OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782400702
OL,3,CNew silverback takes charge after
OL,4,Cdeath of oldest male gorilla in UK
OL,6,F"Conservation breeding programmes play
OL,7,Fan important role in maintaining
OL,8,Fhealthy populations for future
OL,9,Fgenerations.
OL,11,F"At the same time, the gorilla troop
OL,12,Fand their habitat at Bristol Zoo
OL,13,FProject connect visitors to the
OL,14,Flandscape of Equatorial Guinea ` where
OL,15,Fwe run one of our largest field
OL,16,Fconservation projects.
OL,18,F"Here we work alongside local
OL,19,Fcommunities to help people and
OL,20,Fwildlife, including western lowland
OL,21,Fgorillas, co-exist and thrive.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
