FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782400702
OL,3,CNew silverback takes charge after
OL,4,Cdeath of oldest male gorilla in UK
OL,6,F"We're looking forward to watching
OL,7,FNkoumou settle into his new home,
OL,8,Fdevelop relationships with the troop
OL,9,Fand establish his place within the
OL,10,Fgroup."
OL,12,FBristol Zoological Society has cared
OL,13,Ffor gorillas for nearly 90 years, from
OL,14,Fmuch-loved favourites like Alfred and
OL,15,FJock to today's troop at Bristol Zoo
OL,16,FProject.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]
